{"tid":1856704,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"JYP娛樂 及 Sony音樂 合作女團企劃「Nizi Project」","createTime":"2020-02-01T18:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T16:54:11.000Z","uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bd7859ac259d7fbf491b0ced0f42a98f647804fd","tid":1856704,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:20:43.000Z","msg":"日前公開了線上影音串流平台「Hulu」將在日本時間1月31日晚間10點起開始播出由日本索尼音樂「Sony Music Label」及 JYP娛樂共同合作的新企劃「Nizi Project」徵選節目，本紀錄片將為期六個月紀錄本次徵選的軌跡。"},{"pid":"ab9d10bc317dc577198acbc7481d7f326ffb78d8","tid":1856704,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:20:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uZCe6eb6NSo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuZCe6eb6NSo&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXtzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=db7a441c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uZCe6eb6NSo</a><br />\nt寶歡呼Nizi <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f39aa089e31cbe0952dd19b15025a3b75157e92","tid":1856704,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:21:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CMkwZGpHkCA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCMkwZGpHkCA&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXtzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=664b0092\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CMkwZGpHkCA</a><br />\n徵選地點"},{"pid":"eb033d345848102a854a32b3cdb54c7d41d01b38","tid":1856704,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:21:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W5eDu3ZEOiQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW5eDu3ZEOiQ&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXtzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=048f9566\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W5eDu3ZEOiQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cb-deIcmkgU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fcb-deIcmkgU&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXtzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=63920bd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cb-deIcmkgU</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VeLbPuxw5Ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVeLbPuxw5Ts&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXtzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=62977a5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VeLbPuxw5Ts</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UsxafNlqRJQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUsxafNlqRJQ&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXtzIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=7bc688e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UsxafNlqRJQ</a><br />\ns1"},{"pid":"33954d756f6872e5e88b1954fddc39b758600e87","tid":1856704,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:21:52.000Z","msg":"2019年2月，在日本索尼音樂舉辦的記者發表會中，由JYP娛樂綜合製作人朴軫永公開「Nizi Project」，是由他自己向世人報告企業遠景將進入「JYP 2.0」世代的象徵企劃之一，以「GLOBALIZATION BY LOCALIZATION（透過在地發展至全球）」為發想，希望能夠像彩虹一樣聚集各式各樣不同個性的成員並加以挖掘培養，最後能夠發揚光大。而本徵選企劃已經在2019年7至8月開始經過日本國內8大都市、夏威夷、洛杉磯等共10個地方舉辦，同年9月在超過1萬名徵選生中選出26名選拔成員，在東京進行5天4夜的合宿訓練，而徵選模樣及26名成員的合宿訓練將透過貼身採訪節目「Nizi Project」在1月31日起於Hulu播出。"},{"pid":"38ec246e9a57eb20255ce0d2786bb47c6da71fad","tid":1856704,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:22:05.000Z","msg":"透過「Nizi Project」這個全球爭選企劃，希望以徵選生的熱情及想法、被選中者的心境、笑臉、淚水為核心，記錄這些感人時刻，並帶觀眾一同見證「巨星誕生的瞬間」。但「Nizi Project」全球徵選從去年12月底至今年的後半戰，包括在韓國進行為期半年的訓練及最終審查、女團誕生前的軌跡等，預計會2020年4月起於日本電視台開始播出。另外，今後（1月31日起）在日本電視台情報節目「スッキリ」也將有定期的「Nizi Project」特輯企劃。"},{"pid":"675f8f32d7f0d0aa15562adefd9542b77a87190c","tid":1856704,"uid":67294,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:24:12.000Z","msg":"攻日就攻日啦 講到全球化咁做乜春"},{"pid":"313150711f0bc7ff73c64cc6242b0530c794f76d","tid":1856704,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":